Dependency=Geometry Building Type RECS: # Source: Multipliers as a function of building type are from RECS 2015 end use consumption estimates for electricity use other than ceiling fan, clothes dryer, clothes washer, cooking, cooling, dishwasher, heating, hot tub pumps, lighting, pool pumps, primary refrigeration, and water heating, as compared to that same "other" definition from ResStock run `res_national_18_01_01_2018`. MF: RECS 2015 is 5.28, ResStock is 8.02. Multiply current ResStock by 0.658 to get current RECS 2015. SFA: RECS 2015 is 1.68, ResStock is 2.11. Multiply current Resstock by 0.796 to get current RECS 2015.
